{"tid":1949462,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【真.反了】江湖兩省警察發生衝突的真相","createTime":"2020-03-29T15:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T18:52:28.000Z","uid":340619,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62441e12b081012bd6f56d6cff55e3ac688abd53","tid":1949462,"uid":340619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"【江湖混戰 2020年3月27日】江西九江上<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>百名特警和湖北黃梅交警發生衝突</strong></span></span>，據說<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">江西違背中央指令</span></strong></span>，拒絕湖北人入境，因為「不相信湖北公佈的數據」，衝突發酵後，湖北民眾參戰引發大規模群毆，市委書記出面調停。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y5Ji3cc_w0c&amp;feature=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR3Qm_YtINsjgtrGLNHHeu6JzNQcmMu9EIjiZ_DMEDct1PfzJuXsJRFsP6Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy5Ji3cc_w0c%26feature%3Dshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR3Qm_YtINsjgtrGLNHHeu6JzNQcmMu9EIjiZ_DMEDct1PfzJuXsJRFsP6Q&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=7d5d6835\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y5Ji3cc_w0c&amp;feature=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR3Qm_YtINsjgtrGLNHHeu6JzNQcmMu9EIjiZ_DMEDct1PfzJuXsJRFsP6Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//中共官方在宣布湖北省解封之後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">北京卻明令湖北的車輛和人員不能進入北京</span></span></strong>，這並非歧視，而是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中共高層知道疫情的真相，疫情的擴散和蔓延其實根本沒有停止</span></strong></span>，但是，中共<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為了促使各地早日復工、營造疫情受控的假象</span></strong></span>，不讓民眾了解到疫情的真實情況。中國<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地方省市政府在看到北京禁止湖北車輛入境的命令之後，自然群起而效仿</span></span></strong>。這是江西和湖北警方衝突的根本原因。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/3/27/n11981810.htm?fbclid=IwAR2rAGK1GwvMF6hG4PPbRiquvUFUpQ9GoI4a4X981mxbP2H7y_I5DtHwaG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F3%2F27%2Fn11981810.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2rAGK1GwvMF6hG4PPbRiquvUFUpQ9GoI4a4X981mxbP2H7y_I5DtHwaG8&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=1603dec9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/3/27/n11981810.htm?fbclid=IwAR2rAGK1GwvMF6hG4PPbRiquvUFUpQ9GoI4a4X981mxbP2H7y_I5DtHwaG8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/16002c46f2f41fea_ttl7day7Z3_____-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F16002c46f2f41fea_ttl7day7Z3_____-600x400.jpg&h=ead495b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2422bb91ca9d3158307a324ca74bc0b966f4ea1f","tid":1949462,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好期待啲讚開中國用強硬手段防疫&quot;成功&quot; 既 西方&quot;醫學專家&quot; 同&quot;評論員 &quot; 到中國再爆個獲會係點反應"},{"pid":"5f572888142f40c008eb4603e974e6527de4c007","tid":1949462,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db2a79bc27e7d233b391467f9fbf837a4ded9480","tid":1949462,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"北京市唔畀湖北人車入有冇news source?"},{"pid":"82eee0b79aa0ec256fda47e45e49844128738f22","tid":1949462,"uid":301320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db2a79bc27e7d233b391467f9fbf837a4ded9480","tid":1949462,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"北京市唔畀湖北人車入有冇news source?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime